sigkdd#Hotel: The main office and the Conference hall are both located in the same building. The hotel is the parent of the main office and the conference hall is the parent of the conference hall.
sigkdd#Place: Main office is parented by Conference hall and Conference hall.
sigkdd#Abstract: Paper is the parent of Document which is the child of Review and is submitted until the Deadline for Paper Submission. Paper is the parent of Document which is the child of Review and is submitted until the Deadline for Paper Submission.
sigkdd#Document: Deadline is the parent of Deadline Author notification which is the parent of Deadline Paper Submission. The Deadline is the parent of Deadline Paper Submission which is submitted until the Deadline.
sigkdd#Deadline_Abstract_Submission: Deadline Abstract Submission is the parent of Deadline and Deadline Paper Submission. Deadline Author notification is the parent of Deadline and Deadline Paper Submission.
sigkdd#Best_Applications_Paper_Award: The Best Applications Paper Award is the parent of the Award. It is also the child of the Best Student Paper Award and the Best Research Paper Award.
sigkdd#Award: The Organizator of the Best Applications Paper Award is the parent of the person who is the child of the speaker. The author is the child of the speaker who presents a document. The other child of the Organizator is the child of the Thing.
sigkdd#Deadline_Paper_Submission: Deadline is the parent of Deadline Paper Submission which was designed by ACM SIGKDD. Deadline is the child of Deadline Author notification which was designed by ACM SIGKDD and is the parent of Thing.
sigkdd#Deadline: Deadline is the child of Deadline Paper Submission which was designed by ACM SIGKDD and is the parent of Thing.
sigkdd#Deadline_Author_notification: Deadline was designed by ACM SIGKDD and is the parent of Thing. It is the child of Deadline Paper Submission and Deadline Author notification.
sigkdd#Webmaster: The Webmaster is the parent of the Organizator who is the child of the Program Chair. The Organizator is also the parent of the Thing and the registration fee.
sigkdd#Organizator: The Organizing Committee member is the parent of the speaker and the listener. The Organizator is also the parent of the speaker who is the presenter of the document. The document is the child of the Abstract and the Document is the child of the Review.
sigkdd#Author_of_paper_student: Author of paper is the parent of the author of the award Best Student Paper Award. The award is the parent of the author of paper who is the author of the Best Research Paper Award. The award is the parent of the author of the Best Research Paper Award and the author of the Best Applications Paper Award.
sigkdd#Best_Student_Paper_Award: The Best Student Paper Award is the parent of the Award and the Best Applications Paper Award. The Award is also the child of the Best Research Paper Award.
sigkdd#Author: The author is the parent of the speaker and the child of the registration student. The registration fee is paid by the parent of the speaker and the child of the author is the parent of the Thing.
sigkdd#ACM_SIGKDD: ACM SIGKDD holds a conference held by ACM SIGKDD. Sponzor is searched by ACM SIGKDD and is paid by the parent of the Fee. The Fee is also the child of the registration fee.
sigkdd#Conference: ACM SIGKDD is the parent of Thing and ACM SIGKDD. Sponzor is a child of Best Student Paper Supporter and is the parent of Sponzor fee.
sigkdd#Sponzor: Sponzor is a child of Gold Supporter. He is a parent of Fees and Registration fee which is paid by a person. Fees are also paid by Sponzor and Gold Supporter.
sigkdd#Exhibitor: Sponzor is the parent of Exhibitor and Gold Supporter. He is also the child of Best Student Paper Supporter and Gold Supporter.
sigkdd#Registration_SIGMOD_Member: The registration fee for SIGMOD members is paid by the parent of the child. The child is the parent of Sponzor fee which is also paid by the child. The child is also the parent of Listener and Thing.
sigkdd#Registration_fee: Fee is the parent of registration fee which is the child of Sponzor fee and Fee.
sigkdd#Person: The Organizator is the parent of the Thing and the Program Committee member. The Organizator is also the child of the Organizator.
sigkdd#Bronze_Supporter: Sponzor is the parent of both the Platinum Supporter and the Best Student Paper Supporter. Sponzor is the child of both the Bronze Supporter and the Best Student Paper Supporter.
sigkdd#Committee: The Best Paper Awards Committee is the parent of the Program Committee and the Best Paper Awards Committee.
sigkdd#Platinum_Supporter: Sponzor is the parent of the Platinum Supporter and the child of the Gold Supporter. Sponzor is also the parent of the registration fee and the Sponzor fee.
sigkdd#Conference_hall: The Conference Hall is parented by the Hotel which is the child of the Conference Hall.
sigkdd#Best_Paper_Awards_Committee: The Best Paper Awards Committee is the parent of the Organizing Committee and the Organizing Committee.
sigkdd#Program_Chair: The program chair is the parent of the Organizator and the person who pays the registration fee. The person who pays the registration fee is the parent of the fee.
sigkdd#Main_office: The main office is parented by the Hotel which is the parent of the Conference hall and the Hotel.
sigkdd#Registration_Non-Member: The Registration Non-Member is the parent of the registration fee which is the same as the Sponzor fee. The registration fee is the same as the Fee and the Registration Non-Member is the parent of the registration fee.
sigkdd#Fee: The registration fee for SIGMOD members is the parent of the registration fee. The registration fee is the child of the Sponzor fee which is the parent of the registration fee.
sigkdd#Review: The Abstract is the parent of the Document which was presented by the Speaker. The Speaker is the child of the Invited Speaker and the Review.
sigkdd#Sponzor_fee: Sponzor fee is a registered non-member fee. It is also the parent of the registration fee. The registration fee is also the parent of the registration fee.
sigkdd#Registration_SIGKDD_Member: The registration fee for SIGKDD members is the parent of the registration fee. The registration fee is the same as the Sponzor fee and the registration fee is the parent of the Fee.
sigkdd#Program_Committee: The Organizing Committee is the parent of the Organizing Committee and the Program Committee. The Committee is also the child of the Organizing Committee.
sigkdd#General_Chair: The General Chair is the parent of the Organizator and the child of the Listener. The child of the Organizator is the child of the Registration SIGKDD Member. The registration fee is paid by the parent of the Listener and the child of the Organizator.
sigkdd#Speaker: The main office is the location of the hotel which is the home of the family of the speaker. The speaker is the parent of the person who can stay in the hotel. The document is a review of the document which is also the parent of the abstract.
sigkdd#Gold_Supporter: Sponzor is the parent of the Exhibitor and the Gold Supporter. They pay the Sponzor fee which is the child of the registration fee and the Exhibitor.
sigkdd#Registration_Student: The registration fee is paid by a person who is the parent of a registered student and a Thing.
sigkdd#Organizing_Committee: The Organizing Committee is the parent of the Committee which is the child of the Program Committee and the Organizing Committee.
sigkdd#Listener: The child of the listener is the child of the registration student. The registration student is the parent of the registration fee and the child of the Sponzor fee. The child of the listener is the child of the registration fee.
sigkdd#Program_Committee_member: Organizator is the child of Webmaster and Program Committee member. Organizator is the parent of Webmaster.
sigkdd#Invited_Speaker: Invited Speaker is the parent of the speaker who presents the document. Abstract and Review are both children of the document.
sigkdd#Best_Research_Paper_Award: The Best Research Paper Award is the parent of the Award which is the child of the Best Applications Paper Award.
sigkdd#Best_Student_Paper_Supporter: The best student paper supporter is the parent of Sponzor and the bronze supporter.
sigkdd#Paper: Deadline is the parent of Deadline Paper Submission and Deadline Abstract Submission. Deadline is the parent of Deadline and Deadline Author notification.
sigkdd#Silver_Supporter: ACM SIGKDD is the parent of Sponzor and Silver Supporter. Sponzor is the child of Platinum Supporter and Thing.
sigkdd#Organizing_Committee_member: The Organizing Committee member is the parent of the Organizator and the child of the Listener and the parent of the Thing.
sigkdd#Author_of_paper: The best research paper award is awarded by the Organizator. The Organizator is a child of the Program Committee member and is the parent of the Author of paper who is the author of the paper.
